data.description:
Welcome to Coweta! This property boasts a spacious 2,191 sq ft house for sale, featuring 4 bedrooms, 2.5 baths, a playroom, a 2-car garage, and an RV carport with plug-in. Additionally, there’s a 20x30 shop, two storm shelters, a mother-in-law suite equipped with electric and internet access, a greenhouse, and a fiberglass inground pool with a surrounding fence. If you’re looking to enjoy the benefits of a neighborhood while having all the essential amenities, this could be the perfect choice!

Moreover, there’s even more to love about this property. You’ll receive a generous $2,000 carpet allowance, allowing you to customize the flooring to your taste. And that’s not all – all appliances, including a washer and dryer, are included for your convenience. The master bedroom features husband and wife closets that are incredibly spacious, adding an extra touch of luxury to this fantastic home. Don’t miss out on this incredible opportunity!
